item.title: Vitamin 30.11.17
item.contentencoded: Hi. you are listening to Vitamin broadcast on dublab radio. In this episode we will explore an amazing musical micro computer called Organelle from Critter & Guitari. Mans o will improvise with it alongside a tc electronic flashback delay and looper pedal. But we will also follow the dynamic we always impose, the first hour we will focus on the left brain hemisphere and in the second hour we will communicate with the right brain. Welcome here and now.
